@startuml
title UC-01 Register / Login / Logout (Sequence)
participant User
participant WebApp
participant AuthService
participant DB
participant NotificationService

== Register ==
User -> WebApp: Open Register Form / Submit data
WebApp -> AuthService: createUser(payload)
AuthService -> DB: insert User
DB --> AuthService: user created
AuthService -> NotificationService: sendWelcomeEmail(user)
NotificationService --> User: email

alt Login flow
User -> WebApp: Submit credentials
WebApp -> AuthService: authenticate(credentials)
AuthService -> DB: find user
DB --> AuthService: user record
AuthService --> WebApp: token/session
WebApp --> User: session established
end

== Logout ==
User -> WebApp: Click Logout
WebApp -> AuthService: invalidateSession(token)
AuthService --> WebApp: ok
WebApp --> User: logged out
@enduml
